<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>23</hymn_number>
<key>Db</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Pathian nih an zoh lai, na thinphang hlah, Ceu le mui ah an hupphengtu
 a si, A mi hna cu zungzal in a ven hna, Umhar lileng in an chia ta lai lo.

[C1]
   Pathian nih an zoh lai, A dongh tiangin, Hawikom tha bik, Tlantu kan
   Pa a si, Na auh tikah Jesuh nih an leh lai. Va zum zungzal, Amah nih an
   zoh lai.

[V2]
 Pathian nih an zoh lai, chun nitlak in, Na kehlan cu lam dingah a
 hruai lai, Tuukhal bangin an hupphengtu a si, Cerhti kamah him in a hruai
 tawn hna.

[C2]
   Pathian nih an zoh lai, A dongh tiangin, Hawikom tha bik, Tlantu kan
   Pa a si, Na auh tikah Jesuh nih an leh lai. Va zum zungzal, Amah nih an
   zoh lai.

[V3]
 Pathian nih an zoh lai, chan chung nguh in, Hmuh bal lomi a thluachuah
 an pek lai, Caan dong hmanh seh zungzal in an zohlai, Hnangam tein a
 sinah an auhlai.

[C3]
   Pathian nih an zoh lai, A dongh tiangin, Hawikom tha bik, Tlantu kan
   Pa a si, Na auh tikah Jesuh nih an leh lai. Va zum zungzal, Amah nih an
   zoh lai.</lyrics>
<title>PATHIAN NIH AN ZOH LAI CH23</title>
</song>